## Why This Is Asked

Tests knowledge of advanced balanced BST variants and in-place sequence augmentation. It also checks correctness of gcd propagation through splits and merges and edge handling for empty or single-element ranges.

## Key Concepts

- Implicit indexing via size augmentation
- Subtree gcd maintenance and gcd associative property
- Safe split/merge to isolate segments
